        <figcaption>
          <b>Mechanics of Sound</b>
          <span>Built for listeners who hear the small things.</span>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

  <aside class="aaw-about-stat-strip" aria-label="AAW brand summary">
    <div class="aaw-about-wrap aaw-about-stats">
      <article><b>2014</b><span>Founded in Singapore by Kevin Wang.</span></article>
