        <h2 id="aaw-faq-title">Frequently asked questions about Advanced AcousticWerkes</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="aaw-about-faq-list">
        <article>
          <h3>Who founded Advanced AcousticWerkes?</h3>
          <p>Advanced AcousticWerkes was founded in Singapore in 2014 by Kevin Wang.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>Where is AAW based?</h3>
          <p>AAW is based in Singapore and works with listeners, musicians, and audio specialists through official support and dealer channels.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>What does AAW make?</h3>
          <p>AAW makes custom and universal in-ear monitors, including hybrid, electrostatic, planar, isobaric, and Z Series designs.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>What is AAW known for?</h3>
          <p>AAW is known for custom IEM craft, hybrid driver architecture, tuning flexibility, ergonomic fit, and hand-finished monitor design.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>What does "Those who listen will find the way" mean?</h3>
          <p>It expresses AAW's belief that sound design begins with careful listening: to music, materials, measurements, and the people who use the monitors.</p>
        </article>
